{
  "stem": "15686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would go to the theater and to movies as long as Jews were still allowed to do that, because over a period of time, that also stopped.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then there were certain films that could be shown in one of the Jewish centers, only for Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Usually they were old Yiddish films that had been imported from Poland or someplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were not allowed-- Jews were not allowed to see the popular movies-- the American films that were being shown or the German films.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the theater, again, was put on by Jewish people in these Jewish centers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we-- and I read a lot as a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had a very classical education, even in elementary school though further on when I was in fifth or sixth grade, we read Homer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We read the Iliad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We read all the German poets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We read all the-- it was, as I said, a very academic and very classical type of education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was very thorough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- we were the typical German family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was the head of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His word was law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no questioning it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was preoccupied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We spoke to him when-- after he spoke to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would not dare interrupt him when he was doing whatever he was doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother, of course, was a different story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could inveigle her into letting us do things when we wanted something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we'd first go to mother and say, well, you know-- and she would say, well, I have to ask your father.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we said, oh, that's bad news, you know, because he will say no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she'd say, well, I'll see, you know, and this kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
